Package: colorhull
Title: Extract Image Color Themes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jonas",
           family = "Nockert",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jonasnockert@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5425-4992"))
Description: An implementation of the palette extraction part of Tan,
    Echevarria and Gingold's paper "Efficient palette-based decomposition and
    recoloring of images via RGBXY-space geometry" (2018). Needs `qhull`
    and `glpk` installed locally.
